ZH: 这份报告的要点是关于市场趋势和发展前景。
EN: The main points of this report are about market trends and development prospects.

ZH: 这本书的要点是关于如何有效地管理时间。
EN: The key points of this book are about how to manage time effectively.

ZH: 在这次会议上，我将强调以下三个要点。
EN: In this meeting, I will emphasize the following three key points.

ZH: 请在报告中突出要点，不要过多展开。
EN: Please highlight the key points in the report and avoid going into too much detail.

ZH: 我们需要找出这个问题的要点，然后解决它。
EN: We need to identify the key points of this issue and then solve it.

ZH: 这位演讲者能够清晰地表达要点，让听众容易理解。
EN: The speaker is able to articulate the key points clearly, making it easy for the audience to understand.

ZH: 我给你列了一个简要的要点，以便你能更快地理解。
EN: I have listed a brief summary of the key points for you to understand more quickly.

ZH: 这篇文章的要点被夸大了，忽略了其中的细节。
EN: The key points of this article are exaggerated, neglecting the details.

ZH: 老师会在课上提到重要的要点，以帮助学生理解。
EN: The teacher will mention important key points in class to help students understand.

ZH: 在写论文之前，先列出文章的主要要点将有助于组织思路。
EN: Listing the main key points of the article before writing the paper will help organize thoughts.

ZH: 在考试中，你只需要回答问题的要点，不必赘述。
EN: In the exam, you only need to answer the key points of the questions, without going into unnecessary details.

ZH: 这个文件总结了会议讨论的要点。
EN: This document summarizes the key points discussed in the meeting.

ZH: 她以简洁明了的方式传达了演示的要点。
EN: She conveyed the key points of the presentation in a concise and clear manner.

ZH: 请把你的观点总结成三个要点。
EN: Please summarize your viewpoints into three key points.

ZH: 这个项目的要点是实现市场份额的提升。
EN: The key point of this project is to increase market share.

ZH: 你必须将这段故事的要点讲给我听，而不是详细叙述。
EN: You have to tell me the key points of this story instead of going into detailed descriptions.

ZH: 重要的是，你要理解这个问题的要点，然后才能寻找解决方案。
EN: It is important to understand the key points of this issue before seeking solutions.

ZH: 这幅图用简短的箭头注明了主要要点。
EN: This diagram indicates the main key points with short arrows.

ZH: 要在论文中有效地表达要点，你需要用适当的段落结构。
EN: To express the key points effectively in the paper, you need to utilize appropriate paragraph structures.

ZH: 我们会在训练中强调要点，确保学生掌握核心概念。
EN: We will emphasize the key points during the training to ensure that students grasp the core concepts.
